        mission with instruments and contributions directly funded by
        ESA Member States and NASA. Full Table [see full text] is only
        available in electronic form at the CDS via anonymous ftp to
        cdsarc.u-strasbg.fr (130.79.128.5) or via
        http://cdsweb.u-strasbg.fr/cgi-bin/qcat?J/A+A/487/293}",
          doi = {10.1051/0004-6361:200809379},
archivePrefix = {arXiv},
       eprint = {0807.2025},
 primaryClass = {astro-ph},
       adsurl = {https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2008A&A...487..293F},
      adsnote = {Provided by the SAO/NASA Astrophysics Data System}
}



